data.description: Motivated sellers! CREEK FRONT Home FULLY FURNISHED! This cozy 2/2 Chalet offers the Primary suite and Laundry on the main level with a large sleeping loft. This home overlooks Shooting Creek, with clear cold water it is great for swimming, tubing, or kayak about 1.5 miles down to Lake Chatuge!! This stream is hatchery supported trout waters so good fishing. The side porch is a great place for grilling and sunning or relax under the full length covered deck while listening to the creek. There is also a Creekside deck with firepit to enjoy. The home has a wood fireplace, French doors out to the deck, granite countertops, Low maintenance exterior, easy access, and high-speed internet. Was on a successful rental program with previous owners. Call today for a showing!
